visual.name: Tag Cloud
visual.description: Tag Cloud is a visual representation of words that come along with your data

dataRoles.name: color
dataRoles.description: Color your tag cloud based on the value of a field other than Size Value

dataRoles.name: excludes
dataRoles.description: Exclude the tags found in this field

dataRoles.name: tooltips
dataRoles.description: Enter additional field(s) that you would like to be displayed as part of the tooltip. This provides additional context on-demand to users.

key.description: Unlock additional capabilities with your license key. To purchase a license, visit our website http://xviz.com

allowSpecialCharacters.description: Replace special characters with blanks; When used in combination with the property Split Phases Into Words, this will be useful to extract keywords from a larger text like URLs

fontfamily.description: Applied to all the text in the visual

enumeration.value: Lucida Grande, Lucida Sans Unicode, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif

maxFontSizePercent.description: Proportional size of the largest font

maxNoOfOrientation.description: Number of orientations allowed between and including the Min. Angle and Max. Angle

stopWords.description: Enter a comma separated list of words to be excluded from the tag cloud

tagCloudShape.description: Choose a shape of the cloud to be displayed

wordBreaking.description: Consider individual words for building the tag cloud

greaterColor.description: Color corresponding to the higher value of the field assigned to Color Value (if specified) or Size Value (if specified) or Category count

lesserColor.description: Color corresponding to the lower value of the field assigned to Color Value (if specified) or Size Value (if specified) or Category count

singleColor.description: Choose the color to be applied to all the tags
